      DESC="Democracy is an Internet tv/video player.
Version 0.9.0.2 compiles, installs, runs, and complains
This Python has API version 1013, module fasttypes has version 1012.
Then it crashes out.
Version 0.9.0.1 compiles, installs, runs, and Segmentation faults.
